{"tid":2152653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[正視聽] 總辭後建制派係會有3分2人數","createTime":"2020-08-12T06:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T09:26:18.000Z","uid":244730,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0d958e1ac9264f27cd3ee0f42a4ca83603257ead","tid":2152653,"uid":244730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:11:12.000Z","msg":"[正視聽] 泛民總辭後，建制派都冇3分之2議席<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2152391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2152391</a><br />\n<br />\n點解個咁嘅post都可以上到熱門，連登仔係咪個個都唔識fact check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-42369414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-42369414&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=89390ff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Famp%2Fchinese-news-42369414&h=4474d03a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/amp/chinese-news-42369414</a><br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n建制派坦承是因為6名民主派議員因宣誓事件被褫奪議席，民主派喪失否決權的時機下，推出修訂議事規則。</span><br />\n<br />\n2017年就係因為DQ咗6個非建制派, 冇咗2/3否決權，所以建制派先改到議事規則。當時建制派都唔夠70人嘅2/3，但個議案都過到，因為2/3總數係計全體議員人數，唔係固定70人。<br />\n<br />\n所以<strong>總辭後建制派係會有3分2人數</strong>。無論你支唔支持總辭都好，呢個事實都唔會改變，唔好混淆視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a02790126d7f6d2b539c475e8e9e7d937f5753b","tid":2152653,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f8b7889d457c0e8c094c9cb0b0df0a828652ec1","tid":2152653,"uid":53673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"正視聽之正視聽：<br />\n改議事規則係分組表決要兩部份在席議員通過<br />\n同3分2（修改基本法門檻）係兩回事"},{"pid":"45b29a7d346e252f2ac8de7f6bf95c914ebb1514","tid":2152653,"uid":207247,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"總辭啦<br />\n好過比支共撚狗咁狗"},{"pid":"6ef1a8a5fec79c12cbc4914b1acc7e0d351df3ab","tid":2152653,"uid":244730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f8b7889d457c0e8c094c9cb0b0df0a828652ec1","tid":2152653,"uid":53673,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"正視聽之正視聽：<br />\n改議事規則係分組表決要兩部份在席議員通過<br />\n同3分2（修改基本法門檻）係兩回事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:19:45.000Z","msg":"我自膠舉錯例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但2/3都一樣，2014年政改都係要全體議員2/3，你總辭咗就唔係全體議員一部份"},{"pid":"e588b072c4f9b82626e48667a497e1073c66358d","tid":2152653,"uid":91721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"45b29a7d346e252f2ac8de7f6bf95c914ebb1514","tid":2152653,"uid":207247,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"總辭啦<br />\n好過比支共撚狗咁狗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"有3分1嘅話都仲可以喺修憲上面迫佢用人大釋法同埋附件3嚟改基本法，等於送彈藥俾國際戰線"},{"pid":"5bdd480b962471cd6b6ee6a7e1607ec8fd8441e7","tid":2152653,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e588b072c4f9b82626e48667a497e1073c66358d","tid":2152653,"uid":91721,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"45b29a7d346e252f2ac8de7f6bf95c914ebb1514","tid":2152653,"uid":207247,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:14:47.000Z","msg":"總辭啦<br />\n好過比支共撚狗咁狗"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"有3分1嘅話都仲可以喺修憲上面迫佢用人大釋法同埋附件3嚟改基本法，等於送彈藥俾國際戰線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"Aggr"},{"pid":"3b4c5d9452e4f247b08b3f9977073137f63a1c4c","tid":2152653,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"05ba1a134b7bfb686089ec04dea8341d91bc0d50","tid":2152653,"uid":207247,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e588